channel.title: Physic-X 2006 remake needs help
channel.description:
[center][center] [size=18pt]Remake[/size] This project has been in my head for awhile now and i am finally going to go through with it. For this project i will be looking for multiple alright coders who are looking to create a nice and stable server. the coders will be able to choose a certain area they would like to code if they please., a dedicated hoster who will either have a good computer with a fast internet allowing it to be a 24/7 server or a nice size vps, 10 beta testers who will help find bugs and glitches. the beta testers will eventually end up getting a support rank since they will be familiar with the server and client. And finally i will be looking for a web designer. As the web designer you have the right to choose any forum soft ware to use for the community as long as your able to make it look professional. I will not be allowing any nulled software because i will not be getting into problems. Finally i will be looking for 2 graphics artists and video makers. Now i will give some of the server info and goals. What i am looking for in people who are applying - Maturity but i do like to work with people who have a funny side. - Hard workers - And fun people to wrk with The goals that i and the team should hope to accomplish. - A stable server - Some sort of economy for this server - Large amount of mini games including castle wars and clan wars. - Great combat - Strong and fair staff members - A professional and also a stable community - A strong player base - A hard working development team [font=impact][size=18pt]Combat[/size][/font] [font=impact][size=18pt]Skills and combat[/size][/font]
